trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of authentication used for the binding.
trans-unit.target: Angir godkjenningstypen som brukes for bindingen.

trans-unit.source: Values from this enumeration are used by the <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity.MsmqAuthenticationMode%2A> property to indicate how a message must be authenticated by the MSMQ transport.
trans-unit.target: Verdier fra denne opplisting som brukes av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity.MsmqAuthenticationMode%2A>egenskap for å angi hvordan en melding må godkjennes av MSMQ-transport.</xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity.MsmqAuthenticationMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: If security is turned off by setting the <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity.MsmqAuthenticationMode%2A> to None, then the <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity.MsmqProtectionLevel%2A> property must also be set to <xref:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel> for consistency.
trans-unit.target: Hvis sikkerhet er deaktivert ved å angi den <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity.MsmqAuthenticationMode%2A>Ingen, vil <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity.MsmqProtectionLevel%2A>egenskapen må også settes til <xref:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel>for konsekvenskontroll.</xref:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel> </xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity.MsmqProtectionLevel%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity.MsmqAuthenticationMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: The client is authenticated using X.509 certificates.
trans-unit.target: Klienten er godkjent ved hjelp av X.509 sertifikater.

trans-unit.source: The client certificate must be present in the certificate store of the server.
trans-unit.target: Klientsertifikatet må være til stede i sertifikatlageret på serveren.

trans-unit.source: No security is used with this binding.
trans-unit.target: Ingen sikkerhet brukes sammen med denne bindingen.

trans-unit.source: The client and server must be joined to a trusted domain.
trans-unit.target: Klienten og serveren må være koblet til et klarert domene.
